Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started, you can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In today's episode, a car explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The adult world is a bit complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:12.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:54.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nishitama City
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at so intently?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just remembering the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The past?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but in the past, in every bank, there was a space open for the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a bulletin board with messages like "Looking for nice home for kitten," or such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once put up a "please hire tutor" message on the board too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, were you tutoring, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have money, but I married your mother while I was still a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had no choice but to do part-time work to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and Mom had quite a tough time, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the one who really had a tough time must've been the one who was taught by Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? I was a pretty good tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof of that, the student I taught for 3 years entered the law department of Jonan University!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to live in Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in this part of Beika Town often, but it hasn't changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you haven't seen her in a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Megumi Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and her father is a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to let me drink beer after lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, {\i1}that's{\i0} why he lasted for 3 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. What's with that car anyway, speeding like that on such a narrow road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her house is right around that tobacco shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} person got married long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and doesn't live there anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's also a possibility that she's still single!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not thinking of anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come off it. What can I do with you kids along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've really grown to be an adult, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:00.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Beika Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're in shock because it is right after the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but may I ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your name is Megumi Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Megumi Sakihara (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who died in the car that exploded
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is your younger sister, Hiromi Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.52,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiromi Tanaka (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosive was rigged onto the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explosives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the explosive was hooked up under the car along with an ignition device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably rigged so that when the tires turned, an explosion would occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also remember that the car exploded soon after she started to back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I know how you feel, but let me ask a few more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That house you came out of is your parents' house, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents died in a car accident 6 months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's been living there alone ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that car your sister's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the car that I drove all the way here from my residence in Nishitama today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's car was at an auto shop for inspection,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I parked my car in the empty garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not good at backing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my sister was getting the car out for me, so I could head on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She offered to back it out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then {\i1}you{\i0} were the one who was actually supposed to be driving that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer mistakenly killed your younger sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what on earth is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you leave your residence in Nishitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little before 2:00 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything unusual about the car back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time did you arrive at your parents' house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was around 2:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosion occurred at 3:00 sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, then most likely the explosive was rigged to the car during those 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea as to who it may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know if anyone may have a grudge on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was being watched by a man at a supermarket near my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pretended not to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I felt quite uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that man's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a very distinctive face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get an officer who is good at drawing portraits,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we'd like your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't even occur to me that I'd be meeting you again like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew that you had become a famous detective, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brag to my friends that you used to be my tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to track down the killer who did such a terrible thing to Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do that, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise that she used to be a student of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also knew her younger sister too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was still in middle school back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and used to always serve us cake and tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike her older sister Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, who was quiet and easy-going,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} used to joke a lot, had many friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was outgoing and very cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to have changed much to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} graduated from college, she went to work for a securities company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She stayed there only for a short while and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has no children, but seems to be living a peaceful life as a housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, on the contrary, after graduating from a two-year college,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{worked as a free part-timer,}drifted from job to job,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even after she turned 30, still seemed to be living a carefree life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the investigation on Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The portrait is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he look like that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember the driver who blitzed past us on our way to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he was wearing sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his hairstyle and chin look exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks just like that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 minutes before we got to Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at the alley about 500 meters before reaching her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, he could've been fleeing after setting up the explosive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the model and license number of the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a red RV, with a Shinjuku license number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search for it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife? How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but are you Kazuo Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:43.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazuo Sakihara (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a call from the police, saying that my wife had a bombing accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry. Your wife is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your wife's younger sister passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hiromi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An explosive was rigged to your wife's car,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was driving the car in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, have you ever seen anyone like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sure is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigation at the scene of the explosion has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the others seem to have seen him near the scene of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's reliable evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw him among the papers of the case that Detective Sato is handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the woman who was killed in Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only took a glimpse, but he looks a lot like the victim's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, check on that portrait right away and contact Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They certainly look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've met the man himself, so I think there is no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the husband of the woman who was stabbed to death on her way home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from shopping at a convenience store at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:49.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiromasa Takahashi (33)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Hiromasa Takahashi, age 33,\Nan employee at a chemicals company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And over here is his wife, the victim,\NSachiko Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're investigating it as a random murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she was covered by a very expensive insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband, who is in debt, was also a suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he has a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Takahashi's car a red RV with a Shinjuku license plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, it is quite definite that the man we saw was Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he works for a chemicals company, he could easily get a hold of explosives too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A random murder case and a bombing incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they seem to be two very different cases, but maybe there's a link?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although there are no names that correlate in both cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too many things fit in for this to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Another deduction could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a cool looking badge there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please exchange it with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, this is not a badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please exchange it, please exchange it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand that you can't exchange it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exchange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an exchange murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exchange murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, both incidents connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An agreement of an exchange murder was made between Kazuo Sakihara and Hiromasa Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Sakihara kills Takahashi's wife, Sachiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Takahashi tried to kill Sakihara's wife, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sakihara saw the sketch of Takahashi at the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he looked right shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he knew that Takahashi was the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did Sakihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} want to kill Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can be imagined from his remark when he found out that the one who died
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was his wife's younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-Hiromi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His remark sounded obviously more intimate than just a brother-in-law relationship with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate the case with all what was pointed out just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a rush, but are you going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest on charges of assault and battery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's explosives in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Sakihara saw the sketch,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he informed Takahashi to run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that, in turn, was a breakthrough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that Takahashi had admitted the crime, Sakihara turned himself in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and confessed that he has killed Takahashi's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have talked Takahashi into committing an exchange murder
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they happened to see each other at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They never met after that first meeting, and all arrangements were done by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They used a pay phone, so that no evidence would be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara had a phone exclusively for himself in his study upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to have made sure to take all calls with this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be why Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't realize what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what was Sakihara's motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you had deduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara had an intimate relationship with Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s younger sister, Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakihara seems to have thought up killing Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to come up with cash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for opening a boutique that Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she wanted to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dies, all the money that he inherits from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the money for the insurance that she is covered by,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would become his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Poor Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, although it seems she couldn't make herself believe it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All she could do after finding it to be true was cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's understandable, because although she wasn't involved in the crime at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was backstabbed by her own younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check up on her in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the case has been solved and is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help her out as an old friend, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, then, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Inspector Megure.{needs fixgo-kurou-sama deshita}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder if everything has really been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I feel something is being overlooked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:36.33,Character Card,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You promised to meet Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at 1:00, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! We're an hour early!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go have some coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't this the supermarket where Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} mentioned she saw Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, isn't that Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She backed out of a parking space that narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But didn't Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since I'm not good at backing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}my sister was getting out the car for me, so I could head on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She offered to back it out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:59.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what I saw doesn't look like a person who has trouble backing up her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:04.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then why did Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} ask Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} to take her place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:10.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Because of that, the explosion killed Hiromi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can this really be an unlucky coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:18.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:23.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If Megumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} already knew the whole plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:28.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case isn't solved yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has something to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} you know is the Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in her high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could've changed after becoming an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has not changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's what she used to be before!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to believe so, don't you, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But actually she's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:30.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.41,0:24:36.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Whether love or deductions, I'll do it!
